ng_dnd_xchange.m/ng_dnd_xchange()


ng_dnd_xchange()

SYNTAX:

        action:=ng_dnd_xchange(self,called,action)

FUNCTION:

        This procedure which is used in the Plugin-Programing does all
        the Drag'N'Drop - Data things like exchange, delete. This is
        fully user-transparent, that means that the user musn`t do
        anything but the drop!

PARAMETERS:

        self            - PTR to the plugin which calls this function by
                          his own dnd_xchange()-Function
        called          - must be FALSE if this procedure is called from
                          the OWN plugin (normally). Do not set other
                          values, because this do this function by its own!
        action          - Standart-action of this plugin, this describes
                          what a other plugin should do if it was droped
                          down on us, this could be:

                DND_ACT_TAKE    - It should take our data
                DND_ACT_PUT     - It should put his data to us
                DND_ACT_XCHANGE - Our data should be exchanged
                DND_ACT_RUNPROC - our dnd_Procedure should be called
                DND_ACT_DELETE  - It should delete all its data, this
                                  tag could be added (+) to one of the
                                  others!

RETURN:

        action          - The standart-Action of our procedure given with
                          action in the Parameters!

BUGS:

        None known!

